{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01XrzbcWLPAVJQwbuSJ7fJn4","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Scenario Tests\n     2→\n     3→Scenario tests provide fixture projects that run each agent in known states.\n     4→\n     5→## Directory Layout\n     6→\n     7→```text\n     8→tests/\n     9→  run-scenarios.sh\n    10→  <agent-name>/\n    11→    clean/\n    12→      scenario.env\n    13→      ...fixture files...\n    14→    issues/\n    15→      scenario.env\n    16→      ...fixture files...\n    17→```\n    18→\n    19→## scenario.env contract\n    20→\n    21→Required keys:\n    22→\n    23→- `SCENARIO_NAME`: Human-readable scenario label.\n    24→- `AGENT_SCRIPT`: Script path relative to repo root.\n    25→- `EXPECT_EXIT`: Expected exit code (`0` pass, `1` fail).\n    26→\n    27→Optional keys:\n    28→\n    29→- `RUN_ARGS`: Runner arguments (default: `all`).\n    30→- `REQUIRED_TOOLS`: Space-separated executables needed for this scenario.\n    31→\n    32→Example:\n    33→\n    34→```bash\n    35→SCENARIO_NAME=\"cargo-agent clean\"\n    36→AGENT_SCRIPT=\"skills/cargo-agent/scripts/cargo-agent.sh\"\n    37→RUN_ARGS=\"all\"\n    38→EXPECT_EXIT=\"0\"\n    39→REQUIRED_TOOLS=\"cargo jq\"\n    40→```\n    41→\n    42→## Running\n    43→\n    44→List scenarios:\n    45→\n    46→```bash\n    47→tests/run-scenarios.sh --list\n    48→```\n    49→\n    50→Run all scenarios:\n    51→\n    52→```bash\n    53→tests/run-scenarios.sh\n    54→```\n    55→\n    56→Filter by path fragment:\n    57→\n    58→```bash\n    59→tests/run-scenarios.sh cargo-agent\n    60→```\n    61→\n    62→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01UaaUozJ2uL6jqxkwRdUpW4","session_id":"46dcc7a2-447a-40b5-b7b3-893789d3fd2e","uuid":"b51c5ffd-abe8-4fee-9435-a97542573ea6"}
