y, dependency checks, snippet generation, and library deployment path for `lib/x-agent-common.sh`.\n- `/Users/chrisraethke/projects/x-agent/README.md`: published agent inventory and usage examples.\n- `/Users/chrisraethke/projects/x-agent/skills/*-agent/scripts/*.sh`: reference implementations for shared patterns.\n  - `bash-agent`: minimal runner with syntax/lint workflow.\n  - `gha-agent`: scoped discovery pattern for `CHANGED_FILES`.\n  - `go-agent`: optional build mode + package-scoped execution.\n  - `helm-agent`: multi-command command dispatcher + command-specific failures.\n  - `kube-agent`: validator fallback detection + CHANGED_FILES scoping + skip/fail behavior.","numLines":20,"startLine":1,"totalLines":60}}}
